name: First Name (with whitelist)
inclusionRule:
( NAME NOT IN lkp_cities_of_world.cities )  OR
( NAME RLIKE '(?i)(?!^.*last.*)(^.*(first).*(nm|name).*$)' 
AND (aggregate(filter(VALUE_FREQUENCIES, v -> v.VALUE RLIKE '(?i)^([a-z]|\.|\\/|\x27)([a-z]|\.|\\/|\x27)([a-z]|\.|\\/|\x27| )*$'),0D,(acc, v) -> acc + v.FREQUENCY_PERCENTAGE) / aggregate(VALUE_FREQUENCIES, 0D, (acc, v) -> acc + v.FREQUENCY_PERCENTAGE)) >= 0.8d )
